<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="iddd04678b-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective upon the expiration of 120 days after <date date="1978-11-10">Nov. 10, 1978</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/95/630/s2101">section 2101 of Pub. L. 95–630</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t12/s375b">section 375b of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
